smells.name: MagicNumber
smells.description: Report magic numbers. Magic number is a numeric literal that is not defined as a constant and hence it's unclear what the purpose of this number is. It's better to declare such numbers as constants and give them a proper name. By default, -1, 0, 1, and 2 are not considered to be magic numbers.

smells.name: UnnecessaryParentheses
smells.description: Unnecessary parentheses don't add any value to the code and should be removed.

instances.message: Parentheses in (text as NSString) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: text as NSString
Parentheses in (-1) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: -1

Parentheses in (habit.type == HabitType.BOOLEAN_HABIT && checkmarks.getValue(habit)[0].value == UNCHECKED) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: habit.type == HabitType.BOOLEAN_HABIT && checkmarks.getValue(habit)[0].value == UNCHECKED

Parentheses in (habit.type == HabitType.NUMERICAL_HABIT && checkmarks.getValue(habit)[0].value * 1000 < habit.target) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: habit.type == HabitType.NUMERICAL_HABIT && checkmarks.getValue(habit)[0].value * 1000 < habit.target
Parentheses in (checks.size - num) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: checks.size - num
Parentheses in (safeWidth) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: safeWidth
Parentheses in (c) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: c
Parentheses in (k.toDouble() / (nGridlines - 1)) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: k.toDouble() / (nGridlines - 1)
Parentheses in (axis[0].distanceTo(axis[1]) > 300) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: axis[0].distanceTo(axis[1]) > 300
Parentheses in (currentVersion + 1) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: currentVersion + 1
Parentheses in (year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: year % 4 == 0 && year % 100 != 0
Parentheses in (day - 1) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: day - 1
Parentheses in (rgb shr 16) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: rgb shr 16
Parentheses in (rgb shr 8) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: rgb shr 8
Parentheses in (rgb shr 0) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: rgb shr 0
Parentheses in (networkInfo != null) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: networkInfo != null
Parentheses in (buttonWidth * buttonCount) are unnecessary and can be replaced with: buttonWidth * buttonCount
